title: The Mike Rosen Radio Show OCT-10-2013 THURS
description:
The Mike Rosen Radio Show OCT-10-2013 THURS




Thursday, October 10, 2013



Reflection On The" Battle Of The Sexes"

 
 

 - 9AM hour

Mike reviews the "Battle of the Sexes" between Bobby Riggs and Billie Jean King 
which took place forty years ago.



 - 10AM hour

1. Mike discusses the raising of the debt limit.
 2. A look at Colorado's Amendment 66, the school finance amendment.
 3. Stupid letter to the editor of the day on the use of the term "Obamacare."



 - 11AM hour


1. Guest: Andrew Cole, Colorado Secretary of State spokesman.. 
    The Colorado Amendment numbering system explained. 
2. Education talk.
